    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, super dependable, and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won\u2019t let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
