      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips around town. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect if you're looking for a dependable car that still feels fresh. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
