      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain remains precise, and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, with the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Suspension geometry remains true, with refreshed bushings providing sharp turn-in and predictable lateral grip. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience.",
